  "title": "Grafana 12 \u2014 Deprecations & Breaking Changes (Enterprise)",
  "description": "Presentation-grade summary of everything going away between 11.6.4 and 12.4.3 (and the next wave due for removal in 13.0). Designed for an executive audience who needs to understand risk, timeline, and mitigation at a glance.",
