      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:2rem 1.5rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3d1a1a 0%,#a40d0d 50%,#ff6d00 100%);border-radius:12px;color:#fff;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:.2em;opacity:.85;margin-bottom:.4rem\">\u26a0 BREAKING CHANGES \u00b7 MIGRATION RISK</div><div style=\"font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:.4rem\">What's going away \u2014 11.6.4 \u2192 12.4.3 \u2192 13.0</div><div style=\"font-size:1.05rem;opacity:.95;max-width:1000px\">AngularJS ripped out entirely. Legacy API keys gone. Several Tempo and Alertmanager endpoints retired. Provisioning permission semantics changed from additive to full-replace. One-way schema migrations that cannot be undone without a DB restore. This is the honest view of the migration risk surface \u2014 and the remediation for every row.</div><div style=\"margin-top:1rem;display:flex;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap\"><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udd34 12 hard breaking</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udfe0 11 behavioral</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udfe1 5 deprecations (removal 13.0)</span><span style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);padding:.35rem .7rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.85rem\">2 post-cutover MUSTs</span></div></div>"
      }
    },
