    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 27,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#f2495c\">\ud83d\udd34 Hard breaking \u2014 will not boot or will silently break</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.7rem\"><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">1 \u00b7 AngularJS framework fully removed <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Any Angular plugin fails to load. Core Angular panels (Graph-old, Singlestat, Table-old, Worldmap) auto-migrate on dashboard <em>load</em>, but you must <em>save</em> to persist \u2014 otherwise they re-migrate every time. <a style=\"color:#ff9830\" href=\"/d/v12-admin-angular\">Deep audit \u2192</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">2 \u00b7 <code>editors_can_admin</code> config option removed <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Editors lose the ability to create / manage Teams. Grant <code>fixed:teams:writer</code> via RBAC to the users who need it.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">3 \u00b7 Legacy API-key actions removed <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.3</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Provisioning grants of <code>apikeys:read/write</code> fail silently. Migrate every legacy key to a Service Account + token before cutover.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">4 \u00b7 Provisioning permissions are now full-replace <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.3</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">A partial permission YAML used to append \u2014 now it <em>replaces</em> the whole ACL (default Admin excepted). Everyone omitted loses access.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">5 \u00b7 Top-level folder creator no longer auto-Admin <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.3</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Users who expected to edit their own folders can only view. Add explicit Admin grants in provisioning.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">6 \u00b7 Dynamic-dashboards schema v2 is one-way <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0/12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\"><strong>Rollback requires DB restore.</strong> Always <code>pg_dump</code> before flipping <code>kubernetesDashboards</code> / <code>dashboardsNewLayouts</code>. Our Makefile gate enforces a \u226424h backup.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">7 \u00b7 Old UI extension APIs removed <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Custom app plugins that haven't migrated to the reactive API won't register their UI anymore.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">8 \u00b7 Plugin <code>grafanaDependency</code> re-enforced <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\"><code>grafana-cli plugins install</code> refuses plugins with a missing or incompatible compat range.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">9 \u00b7 Data source UID format strict <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">UIDs must match <code>^[A-Za-z0-9_-]{1,40}$</code>. Older names with spaces or dots get rejected by provisioning.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">10 \u00b7 Tempo <code>Aggregate By</code> / metrics-summary removed <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Any trace dashboard that used the old endpoint shows empty panels. Rewrite to TraceQL metrics \u2014 helper in <code>migration/rewrite_tempo_metrics.py</code>.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">11 \u00b7 HA Alertmanager metric prefix renamed <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.4</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\"><code>alertmanager_cluster_*</code> \u2192 <code>grafana_alerting_ha_*</code>. Mimir recording rules + SLO dashboards silently go to zero. <a style=\"color:#ff9830\" href=\"/d/v12-4-am-ha\">Side-by-side demo \u2192</a></div></div><div style=\"border-left:4px solid #f2495c;padding:.7rem .9rem;background:rgba(242,73,92,.08);border-radius:4px\"><div style=\"font-weight:600\">12 \u00b7 Scenes runtime mandatory <span style=\"background:#f2495c;color:#fff;padding:.1rem .5rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.7rem;margin-left:.3rem\">12.0 (locked 13.0)</span></div><div style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#ccc;margin-top:.25rem\">Any custom tooling that manipulated the pre-Scenes DOM (Playwright / Cypress) needs rewriting to new test IDs.</div></div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 27,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:#ff9830\">\ud83d\udfe0 Behavioral \u2014 won't block start-up, will surprise users</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.5rem\"><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>13 \u00b7 Google OAuth HD validation</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.1</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Legacy <code>api_url</code> flows may be rejected. List <code>allowed_domains</code> explicitly.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>14 \u00b7 Table \u2192 react-data-grid GA</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.2</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Column widths + cell rendering differ \u2014 pixel-diff the top-N table dashboards.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>15 \u00b7 <code>cache_size</code> metric split</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.0</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Self-monitoring dashboards using the old name break silently. Map to <code>grafana_cache_gets_total</code> + <code>grafana_cache_usage_bytes</code>.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>16 \u00b7 Single-tenant AM endpoints deprecated</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.0</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Migrate automation to <code>/api/v1/provisioning/*</code> \u2014 removal in 13.0.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>17 \u00b7 Short URLs now persistent</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.4</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">First 12.4 boot runs a storage migration. Budget extra time per 100k rows.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>18 \u00b7 Datagrid panel deprecated</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.4 \u2192 removed 13.0</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Existing panels render in 12.4; you cannot create new ones. Migrate to Table.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>19 \u00b7 Viz Suggestions = default panel picker</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.4</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Cosmetic but user-visible. Announce before the cutover.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>20 \u00b7 Gauge redesign</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">12.4</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">New <code>Style</code> option; threshold labels may shift slightly.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>21 \u00b7 Correlations <code>org_id=0</code> removed</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">backported</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">No more wildcard org. Use the actual org id.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>22 \u00b7 Public dash annotations hardened</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">security</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Annotations now respect the configured time range.</span></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #ff9830;padding:.55rem .8rem;background:rgba(255,152,48,.07);border-radius:4px\"><strong>23 \u00b7 TraceView HTML sanitized</strong> <span style=\"color:#888;font-size:.8rem\">security</span><br><span style=\"font-size:.85rem;color:#bbb\">Span attributes/events no longer render raw HTML.</span></div></div><h2 style=\"margin:1.2rem 0 .6rem 0;color:#f2cc0c\">\ud83d\udfe1 Deprecations \u2014 fix now, removed in 13.0</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:.4rem\"><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #f2cc0c;padding:.45rem .8rem;background:rgba(242,204,12,.08);border-radius:4px\"><strong>24</strong> \u00b7 <code>/api/*</code> \u2192 <code>/apis/*.grafana.app/*</code> namespaced endpoints</div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #f2cc0c;padding:.45rem .8rem;background:rgba(242,204,12,.08);border-radius:4px\"><strong>25</strong> \u00b7 Numeric DS <code>id</code> calls \u2014 switch to <code>uid</code></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #f2cc0c;padding:.45rem .8rem;background:rgba(242,204,12,.08);border-radius:4px\"><strong>26</strong> \u00b7 react-router v5 in custom plugins \u2014 migrate to v6</div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #f2cc0c;padding:.45rem .8rem;background:rgba(242,204,12,.08);border-radius:4px\"><strong>27</strong> \u00b7 <code>@grafana/e2e</code> (Cypress) \u2192 <code>@grafana/plugin-e2e</code> (Playwright)</div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #f2cc0c;padding:.45rem .8rem;background:rgba(242,204,12,.08);border-radius:4px\"><strong>28</strong> \u00b7 <code>ArrayVector</code> / <code>Vector</code> interfaces in plugin code</div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 39
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1rem 1.2rem;font-family:system-ui\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 .8rem 0\">\ud83d\udcc5 Removal timeline</h3><div style=\"position:relative;padding-left:1.2rem\"><div style=\"position:absolute;left:.3rem;top:.6rem;bottom:.6rem;width:2px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f2495c,#ff9830,#f2cc0c)\"></div><div style=\"padding:.6rem 0\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:.9rem;height:.9rem;border-radius:50%;background:#f2495c;margin-left:-1.15rem;margin-right:.5rem\"></span><strong>12.0</strong> \u2014 AngularJS removed \u00b7 <code>editors_can_admin</code> gone \u00b7 Tempo metrics-summary gone \u00b7 Plugin UI extension APIs gone \u00b7 DS UID format enforced</div><div style=\"padding:.6rem 0\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:.9rem;height:.9rem;border-radius:50%;background:#f2495c;margin-left:-1.15rem;margin-right:.5rem\"></span><strong>12.3</strong> \u2014 Legacy API-key actions gone \u00b7 provisioning full-replace ACL \u00b7 top-level folder creator no longer auto-admin</div><div style=\"padding:.6rem 0\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:.9rem;height:.9rem;border-radius:50%;background:#ff9830;margin-left:-1.15rem;margin-right:.5rem\"></span><strong>12.4</strong> \u2014 HA Alertmanager metric prefix renamed \u00b7 short URL storage migration \u00b7 Datagrid deprecated \u00b7 Visualization Suggestions default</div><div style=\"padding:.6rem 0\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:.9rem;height:.9rem;border-radius:50%;background:#f2cc0c;margin-left:-1.15rem;margin-right:.5rem\"></span><strong>13.0</strong> \u2014 Scenes flag locked \u00b7 Datagrid removed \u00b7 cache_size metric removed \u00b7 legacy AM endpoints removed \u00b7 numeric DS <code>id</code> off by default \u00b7 <code>ArrayVector</code> removed</div></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
